event.title: Free Your Android workshop in Krautspace, Jena

body.p: The Hackerspace in Jena, "Krautspace", is organising a "Free Your Android" workshop. Erik Albers from the FSFE will come and give the workshop. Afterwards, the participants will be able to host FYA workshops on their own and will do so in April.
The event will take place in the 'Krautspace', Jena, on 23.02. beginning at 15 hours. Please register before.
